Property.Name: BodyScript
BodyScript
Property.Value: Begin with CTE as (select OrderDate from Orders where OrderID=@OrderID) Insert Into OrderDetails select @Quality, OrderDate From CTE End

Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value: select ps.AGE, ps.Firstname+' '+ps.Lastname as NAME From persons as ps where ps.Age=@Age and ps.Firstname=@Fname and ps.Lastname=@Lname

Property.Name: HeaderContents
Property.Value: CREATE procedure [dbo].[spGetAgeandName] @Age Int, @Fname varchar(50),@Lname varchar(50) As

Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value: Begin Try SELECT 1/0 END TRY BEGIN CATCH SELECT ERROR_NUMBER() AS ErrorNumber, ERROR_SEVERITY() AS ErrorSeverity, ERROR_STATE() as ErrorState, ERROR_PROCEDURE() as ErrorProcedure, ERROR_LINE() as ErrorLine, ERROR_MESSAGE() as ErrorMessage; END CATCH

Property.Name: QueryScript
Property.Value: SELECT OrderDate, Sum(od.OrderNumber) as OrderSum, COUNT_BIG(*) AS COUNT from dbo.Orders AS od, dbo.OrderHistory as o where od.OrderID=o.OrderID group by OrderDate
